Class WifiPositioningService

java.lang.Object
  Service
      de.tud.android.mapbiq.locator.WifiPositioningService

public class WifiPositioningService
extends Service

This class is a service used for wifi positioning. The position is provided by de.tud.android.mapbiq.locator.WIFIPOS_AVAILABLE broadcast having the attributed timestamp, longitude and latitude.
